window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>An updated version of this title was released on 5/29/24. Customer reviews prior to 5/29/24 relate to the prior version.</b></p> <p>Indulge in this duet narration performed deliciously by Shane East and Andi Arndt!</p> <p>Let me just say -- none of this was supposed to happen.</p> <p>I didn't expect the letter to go viral. I didn't think anyone would figure out who Dear Sexy Ex was. And I especially never thought he would find out about it.</p> <p>Yeah, bit of a miscalculation there.</p> <p>But see, I need the money to fund my brand new venture. And Dear Sexy Ex, well, it turns out he needs me to save his business.</p> <p>By becoming his fake fiancée.</p> <p>Yup, that's the pickle I find myself in -- pretending to be madly in love with the charming, brilliant, and utterly infuriating man known as Dear Sexy Ex.</p> <p>Only, it's not an act. And he can never know....</p> <p>The audiobook includes special appearances from Tim Paige, Christian Fox and Kit Swann!</p>"; 
